{"tid":1541160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足戰線","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T18:31:31.000Z","uid":202426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"454cc0b40c3ccfa46c2001fa3d60775f0fd4fcba","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"大家一直focus 本地戰線、國際戰線打輿論戰，但忽略左最重要既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足戰線</span></strong></span><br />\n近排好多單手足因為比<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">黑暗吞噬</span></strong>而跳樓既事，我唔想再見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要打嬴呢場仗，最需要既係<span style=\"color: red;\">先安內，後攘外</span>。<br />\n我強烈希望 每個禮拜有一日係以齊上齊落為提，<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>搞個集會 或者任何快閃關懷手足行動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n除左可以放鬆下、溫暖自己，最緊要係可以令覺得孤單而唔夠膽講既手足感到<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>溫暖</strong></span>。<br />\n仲有既係增加大家既凝聚力、動力去堅持，同埋有機會引起社會、國際關注<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n夜晚10點繼續遍地開花<br />\n每逢星期五夜晚7點，我地會係街頭開著手機既閃光燈 ，象徵住同路人身邊有你有我。<br />\n18區放映會可以加 手拖手人鏈 、國際支持既影片 ，等大家攰既時候有動力捱落去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYcnvpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYcnvpE.jpg&h=1cfadaf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落 ，一個都不能少<br />\n除左係口號，亦都要付諸實行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJS6W4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJS6W4H.jpg&h=a9b0ef28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相約煲底，除罩相認，唔可以再少一個。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n但願早日煲底相會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785b9e37a21c700e6f1e0a72dff8e8ef6ea79029","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f313eafcf15bc1aff500cf7b56380601d86d52e","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56adc9c3f4646ed80cf7f0672d407ded984afd67","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ecb1c5dd1683dd6b78bf9dd03435184e420076","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863a333c78371b0e6f191fca74c8d8efbfdf15f3","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692e934bba50afae82a64c08bb2fca22b8deb750","tid":1541160,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"一齊打經濟戰<br />\n抵制藍絲餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=4103dd20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17</a>"},{"pid":"1c248b5cb7c88e63c5d8ffd3afb1742d0a66c204","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b640e719dbd5f381b28d8c96ba213630f5b2f393","tid":1541160,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2897c417f627d1342526259e71c487751ece38fb","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"大家推上熱門.分分鐘幫到好多手足"},{"pid":"0b133ebdf32e2e92e2f8e39ac18843bd95da1912","tid":1541160,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148dd6a4a20aaab48907a2e91f39ecc1743a1505","tid":1541160,"uid":214113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}